longBusinessSummary: EMB Mission Bound AB (publ) designs, develops, and markets digital slot machines for gaming operators in Asia and internationally. The company offers slot game development, platform development, white label solutions, game content aggregation, payment solutions, UI/UX design, and digital marketing services. The company was formerly known as Embark Group AB (publ) and changed its name to EMB Mission Bound AB (publ) in January 2025. EMB Mission Bound AB (publ) was incorporated in 2019 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
